model_specific_preprocessing.benefit: Eliminates unnecessary preprocessing steps for specific model types
model_specific_preprocessing.example: Tree-based models (RF, XGBoost) don't need scaling, saving normalization time

feature_selection.benefit: Reduces feature space before expensive operations
feature_selection.example: Selecting top features early reduces dimensionality reduction time

pipeline_optimization.benefit: Optimizes preprocessing order and skips redundant steps
pipeline_optimization.example: Avoids redundant transformations and unnecessary computations

key_benefits: Early feature selection reduces computational load
Optimized pipeline order reduces redundant operations
Better memory efficiency through targeted preprocessing
